        "text": "I loved this as a kid and I was eager to rewatch it when I was dissapointed by the Netflix adaptation of the same book. This is way more faithful to the book and because the story is great I had a lot more fun with it.\n\nIn the Netflix adaptation they changed a lot and not for the better. This 2008 is not a perfect movie but it has a heart. This movie is on the on the other hand way too fast paced and the dialogues are not very good. But like I said this is a fun family adventure movie."
